        <updateDate>2013-06-26T19:50:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Stopping Taxpayer Outlays for Propaganda Act or STOP Act - Prohibits the use of any part of any appropriation contained in any Act for print, radio, television or any other media advertisement, campaign, or form of publicity against the use of a food or non-alcoholic beverage that is lawfully marketed under the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
